data.description:
**PRICE IMPROVEMENT**
This beautiful 4 bedroom home is in pristine condition and offers a prime corner lot! If you are eligible for a VA Loan, you can assume the current 2.25% interest rate!!!
The backyard has been beautifully landscaped with turf, an extended concrete patio, and tons of privacy thanks to the added fence.

You will love the lay out of the four generously sized bedrooms that provide ample space for your family or guests.
The open concept living area is perfect for hosting gatherings or simply enjoying quality family time. The abundance of natural light creates a warm and inviting atmosphere with a large corner pantry and center kitchen island.  Like new but better!  Come take a tour and fall in love with the neighborhood parks, new retail and restaurant amenities, and growing job opportunities this lovely Peyton Estate subdivision has to offer.
